olor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexcrazyhorse>AlexCrazyHorse</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/4/02 11:17:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Questions</span><hr size=1> Info like what are some good areas for clerics? Is it hard to play a cleric on FV? Is it easy to level if i play in off peak times?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=taldaydarfv>Taldaydar FV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 385<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/4/02 11:36:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=78.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Questions</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Is it easy to level if i play in off peak times<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
No.<br>
<br>
Low server population here, particularily in off peak times. A cleric is a very very challenging class to play in that timeslot.<br>
<br>
I would suggest one of the classes better able to solo.<br>
<br>
